These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate | sprite | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | bird   | goldfish | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, sports, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, pakistani, japanese
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
4. the dutch is the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the dutch is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | zombie  | spy  | epic |
| Nationality   | japanese    | dutch | pakistani | malaysian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, potato, kale, pear
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, horror, mystery
1. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | pear | kale | potato    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | mystery     | zombie | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, board-games, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, rock, country, dubstep
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the fan of punk and the fan of dubstep##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | filmmaking | skydiving | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | country       | punk   | rock    | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, soul, indie, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, german, mexican
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the argentine is the fan of salsa##1
3. the german is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
5. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
6. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | funk    | indie   | salsa       |
| Nationality   | chinese | mexican | german | argentine |

