4. the french is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the american is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | romance | drama | fantasy |
| Nationality   | dutch | canadian     | french  | american  |

