.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, animation, fantasy
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bus, tram, subway
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | fantasy | animation | thriller    |
| Transport     | subway | tram  | scooter     | bus |

