.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, dressmaker, fisherman, musician
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, mouse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
2. the musician is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the musician##3
4. the musician is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the paramedic is between the musician and the dressmaker##2
6. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the rabbit is between the paramedic and the owner of the mouse##2
8. the paramedic is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | dressmaker | paramedic      | musician | fisherman |
| Pet   | turtle  | chinchilla | rabbit    | mouse            |

