.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, grapes, apple, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, fish, ferret
1. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating apple##2
4. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating apple is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | zucchini | grapes   | grapefruit | apple |
| Pet    | ferret     | lizard | horse     | fish  |

