.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, rock, reggae, soul
1. the person drinking sprite is the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the fan of soul is between the fan of blues and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | hot-chocolate   | sprite | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock | soul        | blues    |

