.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, skateboarding, lacrosse, badminton
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | cola   | hot-chocolate      | coffee      |
| Sport      | skateboarding | lacrosse | badminton | tennis |

