The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, trance, metal, classical
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of metal is in an even position##4
3. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
4. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
5. the person eating avocado is between the fan of trance and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | eggplant  | avocado  | broccoli |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | metal | pop | trance   |

