.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, video-games, photography, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, sailing, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | puzzles | video-games         | woodworking   | photography |
| Sport   | sailing    | handball | surfing | tennis   |

