.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, dancing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | drawing | writing | dancing    | gardening |
| Sport   | skiing   | volleyball  | rugby | snowboarding     |

