1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
3. the british is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the dutch is on the left or right of the british##3
5. the british is between the italian and the dutch##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | singing   | magic-tricks | cooking | woodworking    |
| Nationality   | dutch | british  | italian     | egyptian |

