.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, almond-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: banana, carrot, pear, garlic
1. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
7. the person eating banana is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk       | coffee |
| Food       | carrot  | pear | garlic | banana  |

