.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, japanese, australian, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, bike, ship
1. the thai is on the left of the russian##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the australian##1
5. the thai is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | australian | thai  | russian |
| Transport     | jet-ski      | bike       | helicopter | ship     |

