.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, videographer, scientist, photographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, motorbike, skateboard
1. the videographer is in an even position##4
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the car is between the chef and the person driving the snowmobile##2
4. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the photographer##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | chef | scientist   | photographer | videographer |
| Transport   | skateboard          | car | snowmobile         | motorbike  |

 